#### 2. 精度監視
```python
# 予測精度の追跡
def monitor_accuracy():
    latest_prediction = model.predict(latest_features)
    actual_result = get_actual_sales()
    
    accuracy = 1 - abs(latest_prediction - actual_result) / actual_result
    print(f"今月の予測精度: {accuracy:.1%}")
```

